\c 79
\s Mwari ngaakanganwire vanhu vake, avarwire
\d Pisarema raAsafi.
\p
\v 1 Haiwa Mwari, vahedheni vakapinda panhaka yenyu; vakasvibisa temberi yenyu tsvene; Jerusarema vakariita dongo.
\v 2 Zvitunha zvavaranda venyu vakazvipa shiri dzokudenga zvive zvokudya zvadzo. Uye nyama yavatsvene venyu vakaipa zvikara zvapasi.
\v 3 Vakateura ropa ravo pese-pese paJerusarema semvura; vakashaiwa anovaviga.
\v 4 Tava chinhu chinoshorwa navatigere navo, chinhu chinozvidzwa nechinosekwa navakatipoteredza.
\p
\v 5 Haiwa Jehovha, mucharamba makatsamwa nokusingaperi kusvikira rinhiko? Godo renyu richapfuta somoto here?
\v 6 Dururai hasha dzenyu pamusoro pavahedheni vasingakuziviyi, napamusoro poushe huzhinji, husingadi zita renyu.
\v 7 Nokuti vakapedza Jakove, vakaparadza ugaro hwake.
\v 8 Musarangarira kutirova pamusoro pezvakaipa zvamadzibaba edu; tsitsi dzenyu nyoro ngadzikurumidze kusangana nesu, nokuti taneta kwazvo.
\v 9 Tibatsirei, Mwari muponesi wedu, nekuda kwemukurumbira wezita renyu.
\v 10 Vahedheni vacharevereiko, vachiti: Mwari wavo aripiko? Kutsihwa kweropa ravaranda venyu, rakateurwa, ngakuzikamwe pakati pavahedheni pamberi pedu.
\p
\v 11 Kugomera komusungwa ngakusvike kwamuri; noukuru hwesimba renyu chengetai vana vorufu.
\v 12 Mutsivire vagere nesu kanomwe pachipfuva chavo. Kushora kwavakakushorai nako, imwi Ishe.
\v 13 Naizvozvo isu vanhu venyu, nemakwai amafuro enyu, tichakuvongai nokusingaperi; ticharatidza kurumbidzwa kwenyu kumarudzi namarudzi.
